      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm quite busy with work this week so i don't really have time to go back to the clinic just yet. if it's just a small bit of yellow fluid and it's not really painful, do you think i can just manage it myself with the antiseptic cream and maybe some leftover antibiotics i have at home? i just want to make sure it's safe to wait a few days.",
