      "content": "tea tree oil seems a bit intense for an open wound though, won't that sting or cause more irritation? if i just stick to the antiseptic cream and keep it covered with a bandage, how long do you think i can safely wait before it becomes a real emergency? i'm really trying to avoid a doctor visit if i can just heal it up here.",
